<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  <!-- 교육 수준 격차 관련 -->
  <EducationDifference.stages.0.label>평등한 교육</EducationDifference.stages.0.label>
  <EducationDifference.stages.1.label>불평등한 교육</EducationDifference.stages.1.label>

  <!-- [교육: 찬양함] 사상일 때 본인의 학력에 대한 생각 -->
  <Education_SelfEducation_Exalted.stages.0.label>무학력</Education_SelfEducation_Exalted.stages.0.label>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Exalted.stages.0.description>나는 공부를 거의 해보지 못했어. 정말 깊은 좌절감이 들어.</Education_SelfEducation_Exalted.stages.0.description>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Exalted.stages.1.label>초등 학력</Education_SelfEducation_Exalted.stages.1.label>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Exalted.stages.1.description>일상생활에는 충분한 지식이지만, 많은 분야에서 제대로 된 훈련을 안 받았어.</Education_SelfEducation_Exalted.stages.1.description>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Exalted.stages.2.label>중등 학력</Education_SelfEducation_Exalted.stages.2.label>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Exalted.stages.2.description>평균적인 교육을 받았고 일생에 접하는 대부분의 주제를 이해하지만, 여전히 아무것도 모르는 분야가 있어.</Education_SelfEducation_Exalted.stages.2.description>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Exalted.stages.3.label>고등 학력</Education_SelfEducation_Exalted.stages.3.label>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Exalted.stages.3.description>내 교육 수준은 평균을 훨씬 웃돌고, 복잡한 주제도 이해할 수 있지.</Education_SelfEducation_Exalted.stages.3.description>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Exalted.stages.4.label>학술 학력</Education_SelfEducation_Exalted.stages.4.label>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Exalted.stages.4.description>나는 엄격한 학술적 교육을 받았고 다양한 학문에 걸쳐 광범위한 지식을 가지고 있지.</Education_SelfEducation_Exalted.stages.4.description>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Exalted.stages.5.label>엘리트 학력</Education_SelfEducation_Exalted.stages.5.label>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Exalted.stages.5.description>내 교육 수준과 해박함을 누가 따라올 수는 있을까? 저명한 전문가들조차 내 지식을 존중한다고.</Education_SelfEducation_Exalted.stages.5.description>

  <!-- [교육: 장려됨] 사상일 때 본인의 학력에 대한 생각 -->
  <Education_SelfEducation_Encouraged.stages.0.label>무학력</Education_SelfEducation_Encouraged.stages.0.label>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Encouraged.stages.0.description>나는 교육을 많이 못받았어. 내 지식의 공백이 자주 느껴져</Education_SelfEducation_Encouraged.stages.0.description>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Encouraged.stages.1.label>초등 학력</Education_SelfEducation_Encouraged.stages.1.label>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Encouraged.stages.1.description>일상생활을 꾸려갈 만큼은 알지만, 아직 배울 수 있는 게 훨씬 더 많을거야.</Education_SelfEducation_Encouraged.stages.1.description>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Encouraged.stages.2.label>중등 학력</Education_SelfEducation_Encouraged.stages.2.label>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Encouraged.stages.2.description>전반적으로 괜찮은 수준의 교육을 받았으니 내 학력에 만족해.</Education_SelfEducation_Encouraged.stages.2.description>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Encouraged.stages.3.label>고등 학력</Education_SelfEducation_Encouraged.stages.3.label>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Encouraged.stages.3.description>받은 교육 덕분에 복잡한 주제를 이해하고 현명한 결정을 내릴 수 있어.</Education_SelfEducation_Encouraged.stages.3.description>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Encouraged.stages.4.label>학술 학력</Education_SelfEducation_Encouraged.stages.4.label>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Encouraged.stages.4.description>나는 철저한 훈련을 했으며 다양한 학문에 걸쳐 광범위한 지식을 갖추고 있어.</Education_SelfEducation_Encouraged.stages.4.description>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Encouraged.stages.5.label>엘리트 학력</Education_SelfEducation_Encouraged.stages.5.label>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Encouraged.stages.5.description>내 지식과 학력은 마땅히 자랑스러워. 내 학문적 성취를 따라올 수 있는 사람은 드물다고.</Education_SelfEducation_Encouraged.stages.5.description>

  <!-- [교육: 비난함] 사상일 때 본인의 학력에 대한 생각 -->
  <Education_SelfEducation_Condemned.stages.0.label>무학력</Education_SelfEducation_Condemned.stages.0.label>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Condemned.stages.0.description>나는 공부를 안했어. 그럴 수 있지 뭐.</Education_SelfEducation_Condemned.stages.0.description>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Condemned.stages.1.label>초등 학력</Education_SelfEducation_Condemned.stages.1.label>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Condemned.stages.1.description>난 필수적인 거만 공부했어. 그것으로 충분해.</Education_SelfEducation_Condemned.stages.1.description>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Condemned.stages.2.label>중등 학력</Education_SelfEducation_Condemned.stages.2.label>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Condemned.stages.2.description>가끔 내가 알아야 할 것보다 더 많이 알고 있다는 기분이 들어.</Education_SelfEducation_Condemned.stages.2.description>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Condemned.stages.3.label>고등 학력</Education_SelfEducation_Condemned.stages.3.label>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Condemned.stages.3.description>내가 받은 교육 때문에 마음이 다소 불편해. 단순함에도 미덕이 있는 법임을 아는데...</Education_SelfEducation_Condemned.stages.3.description>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Condemned.stages.4.label>학술 학력</Education_SelfEducation_Condemned.stages.4.label>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Condemned.stages.4.description>나는 교육을 너무 많이 받았어. 공부를 이렇게 많이 하는건 안 좋아.</Education_SelfEducation_Condemned.stages.4.description>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Condemned.stages.5.label>엘리트 학력</Education_SelfEducation_Condemned.stages.5.label>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Condemned.stages.5.description>학식은 무거운 짐. 어떤 지식은 차라리 밝혀지지 않은 채로 두는 편이 나았을거야.</Education_SelfEducation_Condemned.stages.5.description>

  <!-- [교육: 혐오함] 사상일 때 본인의 학력에 대한 생각 -->
  <Education_SelfEducation_Hatred.stages.0.label>무학력</Education_SelfEducation_Hatred.stages.0.label>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Hatred.stages.0.description>나는 인간을 타락시키는 가르침의 영향에 벗어났어. 만족감이 들어.</Education_SelfEducation_Hatred.stages.0.description>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Hatred.stages.1.label>초등 학력</Education_SelfEducation_Hatred.stages.1.label>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Hatred.stages.1.description>사람들이 그렇게 집착하는 쓸데없는 지식의 대부분을 용케 피할 수 있었지.</Education_SelfEducation_Hatred.stages.1.description>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Hatred.stages.2.label>중등 학력</Education_SelfEducation_Hatred.stages.2.label>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Hatred.stages.2.description>나는 불필요한 지식을 너무 많이 짊어지고 있어.</Education_SelfEducation_Hatred.stages.2.description>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Hatred.stages.3.label>고등 학력</Education_SelfEducation_Hatred.stages.3.label>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Hatred.stages.3.description>내가 받은 교육은 끊임없는 짜증과 수치심의 원천이라고!</Education_SelfEducation_Hatred.stages.3.description>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Hatred.stages.4.label>학술 학력</Education_SelfEducation_Hatred.stages.4.label>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Hatred.stages.4.description>나는 지식을 쌓는 데 내 삶의 너무 많은 부분을 바쳤어. 죽고 싶어.</Education_SelfEducation_Hatred.stages.4.description>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Hatred.stages.5.label>엘리트 학력</Education_SelfEducation_Hatred.stages.5.label>
  <Education_SelfEducation_Hatred.stages.5.description>이렇게 똑똑해봤자 의미가 있을까?</Education_SelfEducation_Hatred.stages.5.description>

  <!-- 수업 참석 후 무드 결과 -->
  <LessonForEducation_Terrible.stages.0.label>형편없는 수업</LessonForEducation_Terrible.stages.0.label>
  <LessonForEducation_Terrible.stages.0.description>그냥 최악이었어. 선생은 혼자 중얼거리기만 하고... 시간낭비라고.</LessonForEducation_Terrible.stages.0.description>
  <LessonForEducation_Boring.stages.0.label>지루한 수업</LessonForEducation_Boring.stages.0.label>
  <LessonForEducation_Boring.stages.0.description>수업이 지루하고 따분했어. 뭐라는건지 몰랐다고.</LessonForEducation_Boring.stages.0.description>
  <LessonForEducation_Good.stages.0.label>즐거운 수업</LessonForEducation_Good.stages.0.label>
  <LessonForEducation_Good.stages.0.description>만족스러워. 정말 괜찮은 수업이야.</LessonForEducation_Good.stages.0.description>
  <LessonForEducation_Unforgettable.stages.0.label>잊지 못할 수업</LessonForEducation_Unforgettable.stages.0.label>
  <LessonForEducation_Unforgettable.stages.0.description>그 수업은 평생 잊지 못할 거야.</LessonForEducation_Unforgettable.stages.0.description>

</LanguageData>